anime\\/one-punch-man\",\"image_classes\":\"\",\"link_classes\":\"\",\"link_rel\":\"\",\"link_target_blank\":\"\",\"image_title\":\"\",\"attachment_id\":\"395\",\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/proyectoiti\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/12\\/one-punch-man-2-1551867348.jpg\",\"title\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"wp-widget-media_image\"},{\"id\":\"cfc8d3a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>La serie est\\u00e1 protagonizada por un h\\u00e9roe que ha entrenado tanto que se ha quedado calvo, y tiene tanta fuerza que puede acabar con cualquier enemigo de un solo pu\\u00f1etazo. Sin embargo, al ser tan fuerte, se aburre y se frustra porque no le cuesta nada vencer sus batallas.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"cb1d5f1\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4f71393\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7e9ef21\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"BOKU NO HERO ACADEMIA\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#121212\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Dosis\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":2.441},\"typography_font_weight\":\"700\",\"typography_letter_spacing\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0.015},\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"15\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"7c81cc1\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"237b804\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d373f31\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"wp\":{\"size\":\"full\",\"width\":\"722\",\"height\":\"1024\",\"caption\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"link_type\":\"https:\\/\\/www5.animeflv.cc\\/anime\\/boku-no-hero-academia-4th-season\",\"link_url\":\"https:\\/\\/www5.animeflv.cc\\/anime\\